title: Abbreviated pundit round-up: 'A smell of treason in the air'; regretful Trump voters? Not so many
text: 94 As the nearly surreal situation in Washington, D.C., unfolds day by day, the resistance continues across the nation over a broad range of issues. Just one example: On Wednesday, March 22, 2017, migrant rights protesters demonstrate outside the Hall of Justice against the use of state police resources for federal immigration enforcement and deportation in Los Angeles.
